quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  24,1,"A sura that We have sent down and appointed; and We have sent down in it signs, clear signs, that haply you will remember"
  24,2,"The fornicatress and the fornicator -- scourge each one of them a hundred stripes, and in the matter of God's religion let no tenderness for them seize you if you believe in God and the Last Day; and let a party of the believers witness their chastisement"
  24,3,"The fornicator shall marry none but a fornicatress or an idolatress, and the fornicatress -- none shall marry her but a fornicator or an idolator; that is forbidden to the believers"
  24,4,"And those who cast it up on women in wedlock, and then bring not four witnesses, scourge them with eighty stripes, and do not accept any testimony of theirs ever; those -- they are the ungodly"
  24,5,"save such as repent thereafter and make amends; surely God is All-forgiving, All-compassionate"
  24,6,"And those who cast it up on their wives having no witnesses except themselves, the testimony of one of them shall be to testify by God four times that he is of the truthful"
  24,7,"and a fifth time, that the curse of God shall be upon him, if he should be of the liars"
  24,8,It shall avert from her the chastisement if she testify by God four times that he is of the liars
  24,9,"and a fifth time, that the wrath of God shall be upon her, if he should be of the truthful"
  24,10,"But for God's bounty to you and His mercy and that God turns, and is All-wise"